dct_title_s: A geological map of New Jersey (To accompany the Report on the geology of New Jersey, Jan. 1839.)
dct_description_sm: Principal meridian: Washington, D.C. Geological cross-sections sheet is attached to book. Map shows churches by denomination, manufacturers, taverns, dwelling houses, canals, turnpike, and railroads.
call_number_s: G3811.C5 1839 .N4J4 To locate volume, search call number: ANXB  8565.67.2
